# Testing Patterns

- Vitest for unit/integration, Playwright for E2E
- Smoke tests pass from the first scaffold — deployment gate
- Mock connectors with MSW or provider-pattern mocks
- Test the provider contract, not generated service internals
- Every hook gets a test; every page gets at least a render test
- Run `npm run test` before committing; CI blocks merge on failure

Full details: `.github/instructions/05-testing.instructions.md`
